.SH NAME
same-ci-init - Create a GitHub Actions workflow for your project


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBsame ci init [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Detects your project type and creates an appropriate CI workflow.

.PP
Supported project types:
- Go (go.mod)
- Node.js (package.json)
- Python (requirements.txt, pyproject.toml)
- Generic (fallback)

.PP
The workflow will be created at .github/workflows/ci.yml


